summary: adds a stageoach in every minor hold capital.
descriptionHtml:
This mod adds a stagecoach in every minor hold capital city so that every city in Skyrim has a Stagecoach. If you want the Skyrim Special Edition version go [url=http://www.nexusmods.com/skyrimspecialedition/mods/1021/?]here[/url]. Also if you have Oblivion check out my [url=http://www.nexusmods.com/oblivion/mods/36173/?]Oblivion Stagecoach[/url] mod.

Requirements
Skyrim

To install just download then extract folder and drag plugin into your data folder.
author: LegoManIAm94
